<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Drone_metal" title="Drone metal">Drone metal</a> alias <a href="/wiki/Drone_doom" title="Drone doom" class="mw-redirect">Drone doom</a> - a subgenre of heavy metal and doom metal</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Space_music" title="Space music">Space music</a> - some drone music also fall inside this umbrella genre</li>
